{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":12,"day":7}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"胜利凯歌震云天〔唱词〕","authors":["王佩@"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声春雷震河山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲四海尽开颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大胜利传天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国革命续新篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的领袖华主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席选定他接班。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"危急关头驱妖雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈风斩浪挽狂澜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一举粉碎“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平愤灭害除大奸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽救了革命换救了党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级掌江山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿人民齐叫好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿人民同称赞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿人民爱领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿人民听召唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席，一声令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢下火海上刀山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金猴奋起千钧棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民并肩斗敌顽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王张江姚“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坏事干绝罪滔天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打着红旗反红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴谋篡党夺大权。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的指示他们伪造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马列主义他们背叛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想他们反对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修正主义勾当他们干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这帮典型的走资派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝资本主义跑得欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"螳臂想挡革命车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉身碎骨完了蛋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们千方百计分裂党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种手段都用遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名利地位为钓饵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴上抹糖给点甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁要不吃这一套，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帽子一扣就靠边！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻者把你职务免，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重者送你坐牢监。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是地地道道法西斯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民愤怒压心间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们搞阴谋要诡计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煽风点火挑事端。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"利用权力抓舆论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颠倒黑白造谣言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捏造罪名害同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴谋打倒一大片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把军队视为眼中钉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"污蔑诋毁搞离间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄图毁掉我长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将无产阶级专政来推翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席逝世他们奸笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃喝玩乐狂一番。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满以为篡权时机到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没想到人民挥铁拳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国声讨“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口号声声震敌胆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们崇洋媚外当奴才，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卖身投靠帝修反；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外国人放屁他们喊香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说外国月亮比中国的圆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇唇鼓舌称“左派”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民早把他们看穿："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政治流氓王洪文，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬得快来摔得惨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗头军师张春桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露出叛徒真嘴脸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江青是个白骨精，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凶狠奸诈到极点；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有张丑脸挂油彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是文痞姚文元。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四人本是四条虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四条蛀虫四处钻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四处渴望“四害”除，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四害”一除四处欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利锣，胜利鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利凯歌震云天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利红旗舞东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利大军汇巨澜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧跟领袖华主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马列真理作指南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻底打烂“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"极右实质要戳穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持“三要三不要”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反修防修斗志坚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕征途多险阻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续革命排万难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓革命来促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓让祖国换新颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢枪牢牢握在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永保江山红万年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结一致向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义在明天！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}